snippet.title: Forgotten Seas - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2168260/Forgotten_Seas/
We are a small Indie Family Dev Team, happy to announce the trailer of our upcoming Nautical Combat Survival and Base Builder Game - Forgotten Seas. Please wishlist for a barrage of ocean adventures that await you!
